sentences: Hugo Gyldmark (28 June 1899 - 7 September 1971) was a Danish composer and conductor.

Gyldmark played cello from a young age and his first engagement as an orchestral musician was at 15 years of age  Back in Copenhagen he formed with his brothers Leonard and Sven Gyldmark and formed the Gyldmark trio, which played for the silent film projections.
